msgid "Show images"
msgstr "顯示圖片"

msgid "Displays thumbnail images in the inner arcs and the center of the chart. Images are only shown if the arc segment is wide enough."
msgstr "在內弧和圖表中心顯示縮略圖。僅當弧段足夠寬時才顯示圖片。"

msgid "Show names"
msgstr "顯示姓名"

msgid "Displays names and dates in the chart segments. When disabled, outer generations beyond the inner arcs are hidden."
msgstr "在圖表扇區中顯示姓名和日期。禁用時，內弧之外的外部世代將被隱藏。"
